<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Les Champs Magnétiques - Investor Pitch</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Unica+One&family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;700&display=swap');

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #0a0a0a;
            color: #DD1101;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        .section {
            width: 100vw;
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-direction: column;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        h1, h2 {
            font-family: 'Unica One', sans-serif;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 8vw;
            font-weight: 700;
            position: absolute;
            top: 10%;
            animation: glitch 1.5s infinite;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 3vw;
            color: white;
        }

        @keyframes glitch {
            0% { transform: skew(0deg, 0deg); }
            20% { transform: skew(5deg, -5deg); }
            40% { transform: skew(-5deg, 5deg); }
            60% { transform: skew(0deg, 0deg); }
        }

        .section:nth-child(odd) {
            background: black;
        }

        .section:nth-child(even) {
            background: #222;
        }

        .statement {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-style: italic;
            max-width: 70vw;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
        }

        .content-block {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 60%;
        }

        .cta-button {
            background: #DD1101;
            color: white;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .cta-button:hover {
            background: white;
            color: black;
        }
        
        .image-overlay {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            width: 40%;
            height: auto;
            opacity: 0.1;
            animation: flicker 2s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes flicker {
            0% { opacity: 0.1; }
            50% { opacity: 0.5; }
            100% { opacity: 0.1; }
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="section">
        <h1>Les Champs Magnétiques</h1>
        <img src="logo.png">
        <h2>The New Language of Disruption</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <div class="content-block">
            <h2>Radical Surrealist Luxury</h2>
            <p class="statement">LCM is not a brand—it is a **fracture in fashion.** A collision of poetry, material subversion, and the absolute rejection of banality.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <div class="content-block">
            <h2>Artifacts vs. Uniforms</h2>
            <p class="statement">LCM's **bifurcated product strategy** ensures high-concept surrealism can exist in both the gallery and the street.</p>
            <p class="statement"><b>Artifacts:</b> Sculptural, 1/1 pieces, non-wearable manifestos.<br> <b>Uniforms:</b> High-wear luxury that distorts the ordinary.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <div class="content-block">
            <h2>Investment & Growth</h2>
            <p class="statement">An $800K investment for strategic phase 1: **Art-World Entrenchment → Concept Stores → High-Fashion Retail**</p>
            <button class="cta-button">INVEST NOW</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <div class="content-block">
            <h2>The LCM Effect</h2>
            <p class="statement">"A wedding veil made of prosciutto. A trench coat that disappears. A suit with knees for lapels. This is not fashion. This is language." </p>
            <p class="statement">**Invest in Les Champs Magnétiques. Own the new avant-garde.**</p>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
